 also was a management consultant with ernst  young llp mr hendrix has an undergraduate degree from oklahoma christian university and a masters of business administration degree from the university of oklahoma mr hendrix is a former member of the board of trustees for american performance funds and former chairman of the board of red river energy inc the specific experience qualifications attributes or skills that led to the conclusion mr hendrix should serve as a director include his long history of service in senior corporate leadership positions his significant knowledge of the energy industry and his extensive experience and expertise in complex financial matters gained from his service as treasurer of a public company source matrix service company on    sign up for equilar atlas and view i edgar hendrixs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like i edgar hendrix more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in i edgar hendrixs network and community follow changes in i edgar hendrixs employment and moneyinmotion connect with i edgar hendrix through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example i edgar hendrix i edgar hendrixs connections  sign up now to view i edgar hendrixs  connections » james h miller board member matrix service company kevin s cavanah vice president finance chief financial officer and secretary matrix service company tom e maxwell board member matrix service company jason w turner president matrix north american construction matrix service company john r hewitt dir president and chief executive officer matrix service company joseph f montalbano vice president and chief operating officer matrix service company john s newmeister former vice president corp development msc matrix service company glen w rogers former vice president products technical and support services matrix service company jame