 gogh degas monet i’m not inspired by modern art because i think there’s a lot of nonsense out there”  two years later the spark turned into a flame when jafri went to rome to see michaelangelo’s sculpture pieta “it was the first time i became emotional looking at a piece of art” he recalls “it blew me away and changed my life”  now jafri is a major player on the contemporary art scene and has sold his work to barack obama leonardo dicaprio george clooney and bill clinton he recently created a giant canvas titled the soul of the earth for the  global education and skills forum in dubai the prestigious annual conference that attracts world leaders and thinkers to discuss how learning can be improved  to create the x metre canvas jafri “got into a trance and allowed my subconscious to take over i didn’t have a clue what i was painting after  hours of painting this beautiful magical thing happened that i’m really proud of it was a moment that i borrowed and now i’ve given it back” although van gogh’s the starry night is the piece he would most love to buy jafri respects artists from the modern era such as anselm kiefer willem de kooning and jeanmichel basquiat he also has heroes outside the art arena such as gandhi nelson mandela bob marley and jimi hendrix “i try to do with paint what hendrix did with his guitar” explains jafri “he channelled raw emotion and real passion to create an incredibly energising sound if a painting is not like a jimi hendrix guitar solo then forget it – it’s not worth hanging on a wall” share you may also like edgar on the radio why you should watch wonder woman edgar on the radio when we met djokovic movie preview pirates of the caribbean salazar’s revenge the best netflix shows to watch during ramadan arrow donald trump’s course is making dubai golf great again driven porsche  boxster s edgar takes the new aston martin db for a spin meet our may  cover star zac efron meet the dubaibased realtor selling flats on instagram living life to the fullest why your fatherinlaw will never really approve of you when edgar met fabian cancellara the man leading a crusade against counterfeit watches paris’ coolest menswear store is now in dubai subscribe to the magazine the gulf regions leading mens luxury lifestyle magazine for men who understand that the true value of luxury is its foundation in knowledge not so much a website but an indispensable guide to life subscribe sign up to receive the email newsletter sign up thank you for subscribing you are already subscribed i hendrix  matrix service company  zoominfocom hendrix  molded products edgar hendrix  free public records  publicrecords login  register search options first name  middle name last name  city state all states alabama alaska arizona arkansas california colorado connecticut delaware florida georgia hawaii idaho illinois indiana iowa kansas kentucky louisiana maine maryland massachusetts michigan minnesota mississippi missouri montana nebraska nevada new hampshire new jersey new mexico new york north carolina north dakota ohio oklahoma oregon pennsylvania puerto rico rhode island south carolina south dakota tennessee texas utah vermont virginia washington washington dc west virginia wisconsin wyoming   safe search your search is confidential edgar hendrix will not be notified of your purchase   related searchesed hendrixed hendrixi e hendrixed philip hendrixiue ed hendrix connect with us  matching results select a record below to get complete report aliases has lived in related to   view details edgar hendrixage  ed hendrixiue ed hendrixi e hendrix tulsa okbroken arrow okbartlesville ok connie hendrixcleo hendrixmary hendrixshelly hendrixje hendrix   view details edgar p hendrixage  ed philip hendrix fort myers flcape coral fl richard hendrixdonna hendrixbradley hendrixbrooke hendrix   view details edgar hendrix ed hendrix pleasanton ca   view details edgar james hendrixage  atwater ohboston maravenna ohbrookline machestnut hill mamogadore oh l hen