ens swami satchidananda sweetwater bert sommer tim hardin ravi shankar melanie arlo guthrie joan baez august   quill country joe mcdonald john sebastian santana keef hartley the incredible string band canned heat mountain grateful dead creedence clearwater revival august   august   janis joplin sly and the family stone the who jefferson airplane joe cocker and the grease band country joe and the fish ten years after the band blood sweat  tears johnny and edgar winter crosby stills nash  young paul butterfield blues band sha na na jimi hendrix related bethel woods center for the arts hog farm collective list of performances and events my generation the road to woodstock taking woodstock book film wavy gravy woodstock film woodstock  woodstock reunion  woodstock  woodstock  woodstock  woodstock  woodstock nation woodstock nation  book by abbie hoffman woodstock revisited max yasgur recordings at the woodstock festival  woodstock music from the original soundtrack and more  woodstock   the best of woodstock  woodstock three days of peace and music  woodstock diary  live at woodstock jimi hendrix album  live at woodstock joe cocker album  the woodstock experience  woodstock  years on back to yasgurs farm  lay down candles in the rain melanie song woodstock joni mitchell song authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd x selibr  sudoc  bnf cbm data bibsys  musicbrainz fbcbecbbbcd ndl  nkc jn bne xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejimihendrixoldid categories jimi hendrix births deathsthcentury american singersthcentury american guitaristsaccidental deaths in londonafricanamerican guitaristsafricanamerican male singersafricanamerican rock singersafricanamerican singersongwritersalcoholrelated deaths in englandamerican blues guitaristsamerican blues singersamerican expatriates in the united kingdomamerican male guitaristsamerican male singersongwritersamerican people of cherokee descentamerican people of irish descentamerican record produ