en  hendrix on hendrix interviews and encounters with jimi hendrix chicago review press isbn   whitburn joel  joel whitburns top rb singles – record research inc isbn   van der bliek rob may  the hendrix chord blues flexible pitch relationships and selfstanding harmony popular music   – jstor  dois  documentaries joe boyd john head gary weis directors   jimi hendrix dvd warner home video asin be  roger pomphrey director  classic albums – the jimi hendrix experience – electric ladyland dvd eagle rock entertainment asin bdbjp  bob smeaton director  jimi hendrix hear my train a comin dvd bluray sony legacy asin bfwb  bob smeaton director  west coast seattle boy jimi hendrix voodoo child dvd bluray sony legacy asin bzcfa  external links wikimedia commons has media related to jimi hendrix category wikiquote has quotations related to jimi hendrix official website all jimi hendrixs concerts hendrixfreefr the jimi hendrix foundation jimi hendrix memorial project jimi hendrix you never told me he was that good ed vulliamy the guardian jimi hendrix collected news and commentary the new york times  works by or about jimi hendrix in libraries worldcat catalog articles concerning disputes about rights to the hendrix musical publishing estate los angeles times fbi records the vault  james marshall jimi hendrix at vaultfbigov v t e jimi hendrix original – releases are marked in bold studio albums are you experienced axis bold as love electric ladyland the cry of love rainbow bridge war heroes loose ends crash landing midnight lightning nine to the universe voodoo soup first rays of the new rising sun valleys of neptune people hell and angels live albums band of gypsys historic performances recorded at the monterey international pop festival experience isle of wight hendrix in the west more experience the jimi hendrix concerts jimi plays monterey johnny b goode band of gypsys  live at winterland radio one stages live isle of wight  woodstock bbc sessions live at the fillmore east l